OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA largely
OL,6,Fdry and bright evening in the east but
OL,7,Fshowers becoming more frequent over
OL,8,FDumfries and Galloway. A mainly cloudy
OL,9,Fnight with further showers spreading
OL,10,Feast.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTuesday:FA mostly cloudy day with some
OL,13,Fbright or sunny intervals and showers.
OL,14,FShowers may be heavy and merge to give
OL,15,Flonger spells of rain. Becoming drier
OL,16,Ffrom the west later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
